The paper discusses the challenges of managing and bringing ML models into production systems, which is a software engineering problem. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of ML algorithms to learn program functions, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the complexity of managing data samples, which is related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper mentions the use of ML models in computer vision applications, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
